  <section>
    <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Remember your preferences</li>
      <li>Enable secure login functionality</li>
      <li>Analyze site usage with privacy-respecting tools (e.g., anonymized Google Analytics)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can opt out of cookies by adjusting your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect website functionality.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Embedded Content</h2>
    <p>Some pages may feature embedded content from third-party websites (e.g., YouTube, Calendly). These platforms may collect usage data or set cookies independently. We recommend reviewing their privacy policies.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Media Uploads</h2>
    <p>If you upload files, please ensure no sensitive or location metadata (EXIF) is embedded, especially in regulated industries.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your data. We may share information with trusted vendors or contractors only when necessary to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Deliver requested services</li>
      <li>Maintain legal compliance</li>
      <li>Provide secure technical support</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All partners are required to meet confidentiality and security standards.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      - Form submissions and inquiry data may be retained for legal, audit, or analytics purposes.<br />
      - Account data (if any) is retained until you request deletion.<br />
      - Comments and related metadata (if commenting is enabled) are retained to support moderation and continuity.
    </p>
  </section>

